@startuml Wissenstest_06_Architektur_Gesamt
!theme plain
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F0F0F0
skinparam classBorderColor #333333
skinparam classArrowColor #333333
skinparam fontSize 12
skinparam linetype ortho

title Wissenstest - Klassendiagramm Teil 6: Gesamt-Architektur und Komponenten-Übersicht

' ==================== ARCHITECTURE LAYERS ====================

package "1. Presentation Layer (Client)" {
  component [Web Browser] as WebBrowser
  
  note left of WebBrowser
    - HTML5 / CSS3
    - Vanilla JavaScript
    - Responsive Design
    - HTTP Communication
  end note
}

package "2. Web Layer (Request Handler)" {
  component [AuthServlet] as AuthServlet
  component [TestServlet] as TestServlet
  component [AdminServlet] as AdminServlet
  component [ImageServlet] as ImageServlet
  component [HealthServlet] as HealthServlet
  
  note right of AuthServlet
    HTTP POST/GET Handling
    Session Management
  end note
}

package "3. Business Logic Layer (Services)" {
  component [AuthService] as AuthService
  component [TestService] as TestService
  component [ProgressionService] as ProgressionService
  component [AdminService] as AdminService
  
  note bottom of TestService
    Dynamic Test Generation
    Test-Execution
    Complex Business Logic
  end note
}

package "4. Data Access Layer (DAO)" {
  component [JdbcUserDao] as UserDAO
  component [JdbcQuestionDao] as QuestionDAO
  component [JdbcAnswerDao] as AnswerDAO
  component [JdbcClozeTokenDao] as ClozeDAO
  component [JdbcAttemptDao] as AttemptDAO
  component [JdbcQuestionRepository] as QRepo
  component [JdbcQuestionImageDao] as ImageDAO
  
  note right of UserDAO
    PreparedStatements
    ResultSet Mapping
  end note
}

package "5. Data Layer (Database)" {
  database "PostgreSQL\n(Port 5433)" as PostgreSQL
  
  note right of PostgreSQL
    - users, questions, answers
    - attempts, attempt_answers
    - cloze_answers, question_images
  end note
}

package "6. Utility & Infrastructure" {
  component [DbConnectionManager] as DBConnMgr
  component [PasswordUtils] as PwdUtils
  
  note bottom of DBConnMgr
    HikariCP Connection Pool
    Statische Utility-Klasse
  end note
}

' ==================== REQUEST FLOW ====================

WebBrowser --> AuthServlet : HTTP Request
AuthServlet --> AuthService : Authenticate (Check Session)
AuthService --> WebBrowser : Response (JSP Rendered)

WebBrowser --> TestServlet : POST/GET (Test Actions)
TestServlet --> TestService : Call Business Logic
TestService --> QuestionDAO : Query Data
QuestionDAO --> DBConnMgr : Get Connection
DBConnMgr --> PostgreSQL : Execute SQL
PostgreSQL --> QuestionDAO : Return ResultSet
QuestionDAO --> TestService : Return Mapped Objects
TestService --> ProgressionService : Calculate Grade/Difficulty Logic
ProgressionService --> TestService : Return Grade
TestService --> AttemptDAO : Save Result
AttemptDAO --> PostgreSQL : Insert Data
PostgreSQL --> AttemptDAO : Confirm
AttemptDAO --> TestService : Return Attempt
TestService --> TestServlet : Return AttemptResult
TestServlet --> WebBrowser : Result Page (JSP Rendering)

' ==================== UTILITY USAGE ====================

AuthService -.-> PwdUtils : Security (Hash/Verify)

' ==================== DATA MODELS ====================
note right of PostgreSQL
  **Primary Model Classes:**
  
  - User (id, username, email, passwordHash, passwordSalt, role)
  - Question (id, type, prompt, difficulty, points, metaJson, imageUrl, category)
  - Attempt (id, userId, totalPoints, maxPoints, difficulty, createdAt, grade, durationSeconds)
  - AttemptAnswer (id, attemptId, questionId, givenAnswer, pointsAwarded)
  
  **Supporting Tables:**
  - AnswerOption (id, questionId, answerText, correct, partialValue)
  - ClozeToken (id, questionId, tokenIndex, expectedText, partialValue)
  - QuestionImage (für Bilder zu Fragen)
  
  **KEINE Test-Tabelle:**
  - Tests werden dynamisch generiert
  - Fragen werden zufällig ausgewählt
  
  **Indices:** 
  - On Foreign Keys
  - On type, difficulty
  - On created_at for pagination
end note

' ==================== SECURITY MEASURES ====================
note bottom of AuthServlet
  **Security Layers:**
  
  1. Session Authentication
     - HttpSession Management
     - Timeout handling
  
  2. Authorization
     - Role-based Access Control
     - role = "student" | "admin"
  
  3. Password Security
     - SHA-256 Hashing mit Salt
     - Iteratives Hashing (10.000x)
     - PasswordUtils Klasse
  
  4. SQL Injection Prevention
     - PreparedStatements
     - Parameter binding
end note

' ==================== DEPLOYMENT ====================
note bottom
  **Deployment Stack:**
  
  - Java 17 (Runtime)
  - Apache Tomcat 9.0.85 (App Server)
  - PostgreSQL 16 (Database)
  - Maven 3.9.6 (Build Tool)
  - HikariCP 5.1 (Connection Pool)
  
  **Startup Script:** start_project.ps1
  - Automated tool setup
  - Database initialization
  - Tomcat deployment
  
  **NICHT EXISTIERENDE Komponenten:**
  - QuestionServlet
  - ProgressionServlet
  - FilterAuthenticator
  - Logger (eigene Klasse)
  - ConfigManager
  - ValidationUtils
  - ExceptionHandler
end note

' ==================== LEGEND ====================
note left of WebBrowser
  **Legend:**
  
  → Synchrone Calls
  ..→ Utility Calls
  | HTTP Communication
  [SQL] Database Access
end note

@enduml
